  "texts": [
    "The shift away from checklists and guidelines and towards more participatory methods with increased exposure to stakeholders is likely to embed such a feeling of empathy in practitioners across some domains (Holden 2018).",
    "Practical example.",
    "AIxDesign's AI Meets Design Toolkit foot_10 seamlessly combines design activities with ML/AI knowledge to integrate both processes across various stages of the AI pipeline.",
    "It contributes to internal advocacy by involving a variety of company-internal stakeholders from various disciplines and departments.",
    "To enable the participation of non-technical roles, a crash course on AI/ML is provided."
